<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang = "en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name= "viewport" content="width=device-width, initial scale=1.0">
  <title>Hoodmas || Generosity Corner</title>
  <style>
    /*all css*/
    button {
        margin: 10px 10px;
        padding: 10px 15px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: white;
        background-color: #ff7878;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    button:hover {
        background-color: #ff3b3f;
    }

    h1 {
        color: #ff3b3f;
        font-family: "Sofia", sans-serif;
        font-size: 5rem;
        text-shadow: 3px 3px 3px #ababab;
        padding: 10px;                         /* Add some padding around the text */
        text-align: center;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin: 20px 0;
    }

    p, .p2{
        font-family: sans-serif;
    }

    /* Snowflake Icon */
    .snowflake {
        font-size: 50px;
        position: fixed;
        top:20px;
        right: 50px;
        cursor: pointer;
        z-index: 1000;  /* Ensures the snowflake icon stays on top */
        transition: 0.5s;  /* Smooth transition when toggling */
        padding: 10px;
    }

    /* Side Menu */
    .side-menu {
        height: 100%;
        width: 0;  /* Initially hidden */
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
        background-color: #ff3b3f;
        overflow-x: hidden;
        transition: 0.5s;  /* Smooth transition for opening */
        padding-top: 100px;  /* Space for links */
    }

    /* Side Menu Links */
    .side-menu a {
        padding: 20px 8px 8px 32px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 25px;
        color: white;
        display: block;
        transition: 0.3s;
    }

    /* Change color on hover */
    .side-menu a:hover {
        background-color: #ff7878;
        color: black;
    }

    /* Open the side menu */
    .side-menu.open {
        width: 20%;  /* Takes up 20% of the right side */
    }

    .go-back {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50px;
        left: 50px;
        cursor: pointer;
        z-index: 1000;  
    }

    /*generosity corner css*/
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html{
      border-top-style: solid;
      border-top-color:#ff3b3f;
      border-top-width: 30px;
      padding-bottom: 40px;
    }

    body {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column; 
      padding: 20px 350px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
  <body>
    <script>
      function toggleMenu() {
          var sideMenu = document.getElementById('sideMenu');
          var snowflake = document.querySelector('.snowflake');
          
          // Toggle the 'open' class to show/hide the side menu
          sideMenu.classList.toggle('open');
          
      }
  </script>
    <div class="snowflake" onclick="toggleMenu()">
      &#x2744;
    </div>

    <div class="side-menu" id="sideMenu">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/games">Games</a>
      <a href="/secretsanta">Secret Santa</a>
      <a href="/gencorner">Generosity Corner</a>
    </div>

    <div class="go-back"><a href="/"><button>Go Back</button></a></div>
    <h1>Share the festive joy!</h1>
    <h2>Keep warm</h2>
    <h4>Donating clothes can help those in need â€” don't throw them away at the end of the year, give them a second life!</h4>
    <a href="/clothes"><button>Donate your clothes here</button></a>

    <br>

    <h2>Share a meal</h2>
    <h4>There is enough food to go around, whether big or small, we have something for you!</h4>
    <a href="/food"><button>Get a warm meal here</button></a>

    <br>

    <h2>Volunteer</h2>
    <h4>Want to do something nice this christmas? Come volunteer with us and make an impact in your community today!</h4>
    <a href="/volunteer"><button>Volunteer here!</button></a>

    <br>

  </body>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Sofia">
</html>
